Package DBAccess

Class AppointmentsQuery

java.lang.Object
DBAccess.AppointmentsQuery
public abstract class AppointmentsQuery extends Object
This is the AppointmentsQuery class and it handles all the SQL insert, update, delete, and select queries for the Appointments table.
